1. mvc structure
```
|-- app.js
|-- package.json
|-- views
    |-- *.jade
|-- routes
    |-- *.js
|-- models
    |-- *.js
|-- config
    |-- *.js
|-- public
    |-- javascript
        |-- *.js
    |-- images
        |-- *.png
    |-- stylesheets
        |-- *.less
|-- test
    |-- *.js
|-- logs
    |-- *.log
```

2. __dirname
    the _dirname variable returns the system path to the module being executed